    answer: `${displayKeyword} 관련 사이트, 담당자, 입금 계좌, 출금 지연 사유, 추가 입금 요구 내역을 먼저 확인해야 합니다. 특히 정상기업 명칭을 무단 도용한 사칭 구조인지 여부를 구분하는 것이 중요합니다.`,
  },
  {
    question: `${displayKeyword} 사칭 사기에서 출금거부가 발생하면 어떤 의미인가요?`,
    answer: `${displayKeyword} 사칭 피해에서 출금거부가 반복된다면 단순 전산 오류가 아니라 피해금을 추가로 편취하거나 시간을 끌기 위한 정황일 수 있습니다. 입금내역과 대화자료를 보존해야 합니다.`,
  },
  {
    question: `${displayKeyword} 추가 입금 요구를 받았다면 어떻게 해야 하나요?`,
    answer: `${displayKeyword} 명목으로 세금, 보증금, 수수료, 인증비, 해제비 등을 요구받았다면 추가 송금 전 피해 가능성을 확인해야 합니다. 추가 입금은 피해 규모를 키울 수 있습니다.`,
  },
  {
    question: `${displayKeyword} 계좌 추적은 언제부터 진행하는 것이 유리한가요?`,
    answer: `${displayKeyword} 피해금이 수취 계좌에서 분산 계좌, 인출 계좌, 가상자산 지갑 등으로 이동하기 전 초기 자료를 확보할수록 자금 흐름 검토에 유리할 수 있습니다.`,
  },
  {
    question: `${displayKeyword} 대포통장 정황은 어떤 자료로 확인하나요?`,
    answer: `${displayKeyword} 사칭 피해에서 입금 계좌 명의가 수시로 바뀌거나, 개인 명의 계좌로 입금을 요구하거나, 여러 계좌로 나눠 송금하게 하는 경우 대포통장 사용 가능성을 검토해야 합니다.`,
  },
  {
    question: `${displayKeyword} 사칭 사이트가 폐쇄되면 대응이 어려워지나요?`,
    answer: `${displayKeyword} 관련 사이트가 폐쇄되기 전 화면 캡처, 주소, 회원정보, 출금 신청 내역, 공지사항, 담당자 대화 내용을 확보해야 합니다. 사이트 폐쇄 후에는 자료 확보가 어려워질 수 있습니다.`,
  },
  {
    question: `${displayKeyword} 담당자가 연락두절되면 바로 고소가 가능한가요?`,
    answer: `${displayKeyword} 관련 담당자 연락두절만으로 단정할 수는 없지만, 출금 지연, 추가 입금 요구, 계좌 변경, 사이트 폐쇄 정황이 함께 있다면 사기 혐의 검토와 고소 준비가 필요할 수 있습니다.`,
  },
  {
    question: `${displayKeyword} 피해 상담 전에 준비할 핵심 증거는 무엇인가요?`,
    answer: `${displayKeyword} 피해 상담 전에는 입금내역, 송금 계좌, 거래소 또는 사이트 화면, 담당자 연락처, 카카오톡·텔레그램 대화, 출금 신청 내역, 추가 입금 요구 메시지를 정리하는 것이 좋습니다.`,
  },
  {
    question: `${displayKeyword} 법적 대응은 형사 절차만 진행하나요?`,
    answer: `${displayKeyword} 사칭 사기는 형사 고소뿐 아니라 지급정지, 계좌 동결, 가압류, 부당이득반환, 민사상 보전 조치 가능성을 함께 검토해야 할 수 있습니다.`,
  },
  {
    question: `${displayKeyword} 피해금 회수 가능성은 무엇에 따라 달라지나요?`,
    answer: `${displayKeyword} 피해금 회수 가능성은 입금 시점, 계좌 특정 여부, 잔액 존재 가능성, 자금 분산 속도, 증거자료 확보 상태, 수사 진행 상황에 따라 달라질 수 있습니다.`,
  },
];

const structuredFaqItems = [...faqItems, ...hiddenSeoFaqItems];

const howToSteps = [
  {
    name: "피해 정황 확인",
    text: `${displayKeyword} 관련 출금 지연, 추가 입금 요구, 연락두절, 사이트 폐쇄 여부를 확인합니다.`,
  },
  {
    name: "증거자료 보존",
    text: "입금내역, 계좌번호, 대화자료, 사이트 화면, 담당자 정보 등 삭제될 수 있는 자료를 우선 보존합니다.",
  },
  {
    name: "자금 이동 가능성 검토",
    text: "수취 계좌, 분산 계좌, 인출 계좌, 가상자산 전환 가능성을 기준으로 자금 흐름을 검토합니다.",
  },
  {
    name: "법적 대응 가능성 판단",
    text: "사기죄, 전자금융거래법, 계좌 동결, 지급정지, 가압류 등 가능한 절차를 사건별로 검토합니다.",
  },
  {
    name: "내방 상담 및 절차 안내",
    text: "유선 상담 후 대응 가능성이 있다고 판단되는 경우 내방 상담을 통해 구체적인 절차를 안내합니다.",
  },
];

const publishedIso = new Date().toISOString();
const organizationId = `${siteOrigin}/#organization`;
const legalServiceId = `${siteOrigin}/#legalservice`;
const websiteId = `${siteOrigin}/#website`;
const webpageId = `${canonicalUrl}#webpage`;
const faqId = `${canonicalUrl}#faq`;
const howToId = `${canonicalUrl}#howto`;
const breadcrumbId = `${canonicalUrl}#breadcrumb`;
const articleId = `${canonicalUrl}#article`;

const schemaGraph = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@graph": [
    {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "@id": organizationId,
      name: BRAND.name,
      legalName: BUSINESS.lawFirm,
      url: siteOrigin,
      logo: assetUrl(BRAND.logo),
      image: ogImageUrl,
      telephone: BRAND.phone,
      address: {
        "@type": "PostalAddress",
        addressCountry: "KR",
        addressRegion: "서울특별시",
        addressLocality: "강남구",
        streetAddress: BUSINESS.address,
      },
      contactPoint: [
        {
          "@type": "ContactPoint",
          contactType: "customer support",
          telephone: BRAND.phone,
          availableLanguage: ["ko-KR"],
          areaServed: "KR",
        },
      ],
    },
    {
      "@type": "WebSite",
      "@id": websiteId,
      url: siteOrigin,
      name: BRAND.name,
      inLanguage: "ko-KR",
      publisher: {
        "@id": organizationId,
      },
    },
    {
      "@type": "LegalService",
      "@id": legalServiceId,
      name: BRAND.name,
      legalName: BUSINESS.lawFirm,
      url: siteOrigin,
      image: ogImageUrl,
      telephone: BRAND.phone,
      areaServed: "KR",
      priceRange: "상담 후 안내",
      address: {
        "@type": "PostalAddress",
        addressCountry: "KR",
        addressRegion: "서울특별시",
        addressLocality: "강남구",
        streetAddress: BUSINESS.address,
      },
      parentOrganization: {
        "@id": organizationId,
      },
      employee: {
        "@type": "Person",
        name: BUSINESS.responsibleLawyer,
        jobTitle: "광고책임변호사",
        worksFor: {
          "@id": organizationId,
        },
      },
      knowsAbout: [
        "금융사기",
        "사칭 사기",
        "출금 지연",
        "추가 입금 요구",
        "대포통장",
        "피해금 회수",
        primaryTopic,
      ],
    },
    {
      "@type": "WebPage",
      "@id": webpageId,
      url: canonicalUrl,
      name: pageTitle,
      headline: seoHeadline,
      description: pageDescription,
      inLanguage: "ko-KR",
      datePublished: publishedIso,
      dateModified: publishedIso,
      isPartOf: {
        "@id": websiteId,
      },
      about: {
        "@id": legalServiceId,
      },
      primaryImageOfPage: {
        "@type": "ImageObject",
        url: ogImageUrl,
        width: 1200,
        height: 630,
      },
      breadcrumb: {
        "@id": breadcrumbId,
      },
      mainEntity: [
        {
          "@id": faqId,
        },
        {
          "@id": howToId,
        },
      ],
    },
    {
      "@type": "Article",
      "@id": articleId,
      mainEntityOfPage: {
        "@id": webpageId,
      },
      headline: seoHeadline,
      description: seoSummary,
      image: ogImageUrl,
      author: {
        "@id": organizationId,
      },
      publisher: {
        "@id": organizationId,
      },
      datePublished: publishedIso,
      dateModified: publishedIso,
      inLanguage: "ko-KR",
      articleSection: "금융사기 사칭 피해 긴급 대응",
      keywords: metaKeywords,
      about: [
        primaryTopic,
        ...seoKeywordVariants,
        "정상기업 사칭",
        "법무법인 사칭 2차 피해",
        "출금 지연",
        "추가 입금 요구",
        "대포통장",
      ],
      mentions: seoKeywordVariants.map((name) => ({
        "@type": "Thing",
        name,
      })),
    },
    {
      "@type": "FAQPage",
      "@id": faqId,
      mainEntity: structuredFaqItems.map((item) => ({
        "@type": "Question",
        name: item.question,
        acceptedAnswer: {
          "@type": "Answer",
          text: item.answer,
        },
      })),
    },
    {
      "@type": "HowTo",
      "@id": howToId,
      name: hasKeyword
        ? `${displayKeyword} 사칭 사기 초기 대응 절차`
        : "금융사기 및 사칭 피해 초기 대응 절차",
      description: `${displayKeyword} 관련 피해 정황 발생 시 증거 보존, 계좌 확인, 법적 대응 가능성 검토, 내방 상담 순서로 대응합니다.`,
      totalTime: "PT30M",
      supply: [
        {
          "@type": "HowToSupply",
          name: "입금내역",
        },
        {
          "@type": "HowToSupply",
          name: "계좌번호 및 거래내역",
        },
        {
          "@type": "HowToSupply",
          name: "대화자료 및 사이트 화면",
        },
      ],
      step: howToSteps.map((step, index) => ({
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        position: index + 1,
        name: step.name,
        text: step.text,
      })),
    },
    {
      "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
      "@id": breadcrumbId,
      itemListElement: [
        {
          "@type": "ListItem",
          position: 1,
          name: BRAND.name,
          item: siteOrigin,
        },
        {
          "@type": "ListItem",
          position: 2,
          name: hasKeyword ? `${displayKeyword} 사칭 사기` : "긴급 안내 페이지",
          item: canonicalUrl,
        },
      ],
    },
    {
      "@type": "ItemList",
      "@id": `${canonicalUrl}#keyword-list`,
      name: `${displayKeyword} 관련 피해 검색 주제`,
      itemListElement: seoKeywordVariants.map((name, index) => ({
        "@type": "ListItem",
        position: index + 1,
        name,
        url: canonicalUrl,
      })),
    },
  ],
};
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={pageDescription} />
    <meta name="keywords" content={metaKeywords} />
    <meta name="author" content={BRAND.name} />
    <meta name="publisher" content={BRAND.name} />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow, max-image-preview:large, max-snippet:-1, max-video-preview:-1" />
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=yes" />
    <link rel="canonical" href={canonicalUrl} />
    <link rel="alternate" hreflang="ko-KR" href={canonicalUrl} />

    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href={faviconUrl} />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="192x192" href={faviconUrl} />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href={appleTouchIconUrl} />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#050506" />

    <meta property="og:locale" content="ko_KR" />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content={BRAND.name} />
    <meta property="og:title" content={pageTitle} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={pageDescription} />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content={canonicalUrl} />
    <meta property="og:image" content={ogImageUrl} />
    <meta property="og:image:secure_url" content={ogImageUrl} />
    <meta property="og:image:type" content="image/png" />
    <meta property="og:image:width" content="1200" />
    <meta property="og:image:height" content="630" />
    <meta property="og:image:alt" content={`${BRAND.name} 금융사기 긴급 상담 안내`} />

    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content={pageTitle} />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content={pageDescription} />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content={ogImageUrl} />

    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schemaGraph)} />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      crossorigin
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard/dist/web/static/pretendard.css"
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="page-shell">
      <div class="top-alert">
        <span class="alert-dot"></span>
        현재 <strong>{displayKeyword}</strong> 관련 사칭 피해 문의가 증가하여 긴급 안내 페이지가 개설되었습니다.
      </div>

      <main>
        <section class="hero section">
          <div class="hero-bg">
            <video
              class="hero-video"
              src="/videos/gangnam-night.mp4"
              autoplay
              muted
              loop
              playsinline
              preload="metadata"
              aria-hidden="true"
            ></video>
            <div class="hero-video-overlay"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-copy">
            <div class="hero-brand-mark" aria-label="법무법인 윤빛 로고">
              <img src={BRAND.logo} alt="법무법인 윤빛" loading="eager" />
            </div>

            <p class="pill-eyebrow">{todayLabel} · 현재 접수 가능 · 금융사기 긴급 대응</p>

            <h1>
              <span>{displayKeyword} 사칭 사기</span>
              지금 이 순간이<br>
              골든타임일 수 있습니다
            </h1>

            <div class="question-list" aria-label="피해 의심 정황">
              <p>출금이 계속 지연되고 있습니까?</p>
              <p>세금·수수료·보증금 명목으로<br class="mobile-only" /> 추가 입금을 요구받고 있습니까?</p>
              <p>담당자와 연락이 끊겼습니까?</p>
              <p>사이트 또는 앱 접속이 막혔습니까?</p>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-warning">
              <strong>위 상황 중 하나라도 해당된다면 단순한 오류가 아닐 수 있습니다.</strong>
              <span>
                이는 전형적인 금융사기 피해 패턴 중 하나입니다. 자금이 여러 계좌로 분산·세탁되기 전
                신속한 법적 대응이 이루어질수록 원금 회수 가능성이 높아집니다.
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section flow-section">
          <div class="section-head">
            <p class="eyebrow">범죄수익 이동 정황</p>
            <h2>피해금은 한 계좌에 오래 머무르지 않습니다</h2>
            <p>
              피해금이 입금되는 순간, 사기 조직은 자금을 수취 계좌에서 여러 계좌로 빠르게 분산시킵니다.
              이후 대포통장, 인출책, 가상자산 전환 등을 거쳐 자금 추적을 어렵게 만들고 현금화·은닉을 시도합니다.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="flow-alert">
            초기 48시간 내 대응이 늦어질수록 피해금 회수 가능성은 낮아질 수 있습니다.
          </div>

          <div class="vertical-flow" aria-label="범죄수익 이동 흐름">
            {flowSteps.map((item, index) => (
              <Fragment>
                <article class="flow-card">
                  <span>{String(index + 1).padStart(2, "0")}</span>
                  <h3>{item.title}</h3>
                  <p>{item.text}</p>
                </article>
                {index < flowSteps.length - 1 && <div class="down-arrow">↓</div>}
              </Fragment>
            ))}
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section case-section">
          <div class="section-head">
            <p class="eyebrow">성공 사례 · 골든타임</p>
            <h2>같은 피해라도, 대응 시점에 따라 결과는 달라질 수 있습니다.</h2>
            <p>
              피해금이 여러 계좌로 분산되기 전 입금 계좌, 거래내역, 대화자료를 확보하고
              초기 법적 대응에 들어간 사례일수록 자금 흐름을 추적하고 차단하는 데 유리한 대응 구조를 만들 수 있습니다.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="golden-time-panel">
            <strong>핵심은 골든타임 내 정확한 대응입니다.</strong>
          </div>

          <div class="case-marquee-shell" aria-label="초기 대응 사례 자동 롤링">
            <div class="case-marquee-track">
              {agreementLoop.map((item, index) => (
                <article class="case-card" aria-hidden={index >= agreements.length}>
                  <div class="case-image">
                    <img src={item.image} alt={`${item.title} 이미지`} loading="lazy" />
                    <span class="image-fallback">합의서 이미지</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="case-body">
                    <strong>{item.title}</strong>
                    <span>{item.meta}</span>
                    <p>{item.text}</p>
                  </div>
                </article>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="media-block">
            <div class="section-head compact">
              <p class="eyebrow">언론 보도로 확인된 윤빛의 금융사기 대응 체계</p>
              <h2>피해금 회복의 차이는 초기 대응 구조에서 갈립니다.</h2>
              <p>
                법무법인 윤빛은 반복되는 금융사기 사건에서 입금 계좌와 자금 흐름을 빠르게 분석해
                다수의 피해금 회복 사례를 만들어왔습니다.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="media-news-panel" aria-label="언론 송출 기사 목록">
              {mediaReleases.map((item) => (
                <a class="media-news-item" href={item.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  <div class="media-news-copy">
                    <div class="media-news-meta">
                      <span class="press-dot"></span>
                      <strong>{item.press}</strong>
                      <span>·</span>
                      <time>{item.date}</time>
                    </div>
                    <h3>{item.title}</h3>
                    <p>{item.excerpt}</p>
                  </div>
                  <span class="media-open-label">기사 보기 <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span></span>
                </a>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section procedure-section">
          <div class="section-head">
            <p class="eyebrow">윤빛 절차 · 자금 추적 노하우</p>
            <h2>
              <span>{displayKeyword} 사칭 사기</span>
              형식적인 절차에 그치지 않고, 자금 이동 가능성까지 함께 봅니다
            </h2>
            <p>
              법무법인 윤빛은 단순히 피해 사실만 정리하지 않습니다.
              운영 패턴과 자금 이동 구조를 종합해 대응 우선순위를 함께 정리합니다.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="procedure-grid">
            {yoonbitProcess.map((item) => (
              <article class="procedure-card">
                <span>{item.step}</span>
                <h3>{item.title}</h3>
                <p>{item.text}</p>
              </article>
            ))}
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section legal-section">
          <div class="legal-panel">
            <div class="section-head compact">
              <p class="eyebrow">법적 근거 · 가능한 조치</p>
              <h2>{displayKeyword} 사칭 사기는 형사 고소와 피해금 회복 절차가 함께 움직입니다.</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="legal-basis-grid">
              {legalBases.map((base) => (
                <article class="legal-basis-card">
                  <h3>{base.title}</h3>
                  <p>{base.text}</p>
                </article>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section consult-section" id="consult">
          <div class="section-head">
            <p class="eyebrow">24시 연중무휴 무료 상담 접수</p>
            <h2>
              <span>{displayKeyword} 사칭 사기,</span>
              지금 접수하지 않으면 대응 시점이 늦어질 수 있습니다.
            </h2>
            <p>상담 신청을 남겨주시면 전담팀이 접수 내용을 확인한 뒤 10분 이내 연락드립니다.</p>
          </div>

          <form class="consult-form" id="consultForm" data-keyword={displayKeyword} data-page-url={canonicalUrl}>
            <input class="hp-field" type="text" name="website" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" aria-hidden="true" />
            <label>
              이름
              <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="성함을 입력해주세요" required />
            </label>

            <label>
              연락처
              <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="10분 내 연락 가능한 번호" required />
            </label>

            <label>
              피해 업체명
              <input type="text" name="company" placeholder={`${displayKeyword} 사칭 사기 업체명 또는 사이트명`} />
            </label>

            <label>
              입금 금액
              <input type="text" name="amount" placeholder="예: 3,000만 원" />
            </label>

            <button type="submit">24시 긴급 상담 신청하기</button>

            <p class="form-notice">
              24시간 연중무휴 접수 가능하며, 접수 후 순차적으로 연락드립니다.<br />
              구체적인 진행 가능 여부는 사건 자료 확인 후 안내됩니다.
            </p>

            <p class="form-status" id="consultFormStatus" aria-live="polite"></p>
          </form>
        </section>

        <section class="section faq-section" id="faq">
          <div class="section-head">
            <p class="eyebrow">자주 묻는 질문 · 피해 초기 확인</p>
            <h2>
              <span>{displayKeyword} 사칭 사기</span>
              상담 전 가장 많이 확인하는 질문입니다
            </h2>
            <p>
              출금 지연, 추가 입금 요구, 계좌 변경, 연락두절 정황은 서로 연결되어 나타나는 경우가 많습니다.
              아래 항목을 기준으로 현재 상황을 먼저 정리해보세요.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-grid" aria-label={`${displayKeyword} 사칭 사기 자주 묻는 질문`}>
            {faqItems.map((item, index) => (
              <article class="faq-card">
                <span>{String(index + 1).padStart(2, "0")}</span>
                <h3>{item.question}</h3>
                <p>{item.answer}</p>
              </article>
            ))}
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>

      <footer class="compliance-footer" aria-label="법무법인 윤빛 고지 및 사업자 정보">
        <div class="footer-inner">
          <section class="footer-notice-panel" aria-label="사칭 피해 및 상담 절차 고지">
            <p class="footer-kicker">사칭 피해 예방 및 상담 절차 고지</p>
            <div class="footer-notice-copy">
              {footerNotice.map((notice) => (
                <p>{notice}</p>
              ))}
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="business-panel" aria-label="법무법인 윤빛 사업자 정보">
            <dl class="business-list">
              <div>
                <dt>상호</dt>
                <dd>{BUSINESS.lawFirm}</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt>광고책임변호사</dt>
                <dd>{BUSINESS.responsibleLawyer}</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt>사업자등록번호</dt>
                <dd>{BUSINESS.businessNumber}</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt>주소</dt>
                <dd>{BUSINESS.address}</dd>
              </div>
            </dl>

            <nav class="policy-links" aria-label="정책 안내">
              <a href="/privacy">개인정보처리방침</a>
              <a href="/terms">이용약관</a>
              <a href="/disclaimer">면책고지</a>
            </nav>
          </section>
        </div>
      </footer>

      <div class="bottom-cta" aria-label="하단 긴급 상담">
        <div>
          <strong>{displayKeyword} 사칭 사기 긴급 접수</strong>
          <span>24시 무료 상담 ☎️ {BRAND.phone}</span>
        </div>
        <nav>
          <a href={BRAND.tel}>전화 상담</a>
          <a href={BRAND.kakao} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">카카오 상담</a>
          <a href="#consult">상담 신청</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>

    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #050506;
        --card: rgba(19, 19, 23, 0.72);
        --line: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.105);
        --line-red: rgba(170, 34, 44, 0.34);
        --red: #8f121b;
        --red2: #b9222c;
        --gold: #cfa86c;
        --gold-soft: #e7c895;
        --text: #f5f0eb;
        --muted: #bbb0aa;
        --dim: #817872;
        --max: 1160px;
        --radius-xl: 32px;
        --radius-lg: 24px;
        --radius-md: 16px;
        --shadow: 0 24px 78px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-width: 320px;
        color: var(--text);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 50% -10%, rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.21), transparent 34%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 12% 20%, rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.055), transparent 30%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 88% 16%, rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.08), transparent 32%),
          linear-gradient(135deg, #020202 0%, #07080b 44%, #110607 100%);
        font-family:
          "Pretendard",
          "Apple SD Gothic Neo",
          "Noto Sans KR",
          -apple-system,
          BlinkMacSystemFont,
          sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.68;
        word-break: keep-all;
        overflow-x: hidden;
        text-align: center;
        letter-spacing: -0.032em;
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      body::before {
        content: "";
        position: fixed;
        inset: 0;
        z-index: -1;
        pointer-events: none;
        background-image:
          linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.013) 1px, transparent 1px),
          linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.013) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 52px 52px;
        mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.66), transparent 82%);
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      img {
        display: block;
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      h1,
      h2,
      h3,
      p {
        margin-top: 0;
      }

      .page-shell {
        min-height: 100vh;
        padding-top: 42px;
        padding-bottom: 104px;
        overflow: hidden;
        position: relative;
      }

      .top-alert {
        position: fixed;
        left: 0;
        top: 0;
        width: 100%;
        z-index: 90;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 10px 16px;
        color: #fff2ef;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 430;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(72, 8, 14, 0.88), rgba(22, 8, 12, 0.9));
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
        backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      }

      .top-alert strong {
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 650;
      }

      .alert-dot {
        width: 7px;
        height: 7px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #ec4450;
        box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(236, 68, 80, 0.74);
        flex: 0 0 auto;
      }

      .section {
        width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 36px));
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 86px 0;
        position: relative;
      }

      .section + .section {
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.045);
      }

      .hero {
        min-height: 690px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        padding-top: 48px;
        padding-bottom: 78px;
        border-top: 0;
      }

      .hero-bg {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0 50%;
        width: 100vw;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        z-index: -1;
        overflow: hidden;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 50% 22%, rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.18), transparent 38%),
          linear-gradient(135deg, #040405, #160607);
      }

      .hero-video {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        filter: brightness(0.76) contrast(1.08) saturate(1.05);
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scale(1.02);
      }

      .hero-video-overlay {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background:
          linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(5, 5, 6, 0.34), rgba(5, 5, 6, 0.22) 42%, rgba(5, 5, 6, 0.58)),
          linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(5, 5, 6, 0.48), rgba(5, 5, 6, 0.13) 50%, rgba(5, 5, 6, 0.48)),
          radial-gradient(circle at 50% 18%, rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.1), transparent 38%);
      }

      .hero-copy {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 940px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .hero-brand-mark {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .hero-brand-mark img {
        width: auto;
        max-width: min(460px, 72vw);
        height: clamp(88px, 11vw, 136px);
        object-fit: contain;
        filter: drop-shadow(0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.42));
      }

      .eyebrow,
      .pill-eyebrow {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        color: var(--gold);
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 560;
        letter-spacing: -0.006em;
      }

      .pill-eyebrow {
        display: inline-flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 8px 15px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.21);
        border: 1px solid rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.23);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 34px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }

      h1 {
        margin-bottom: 28px;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: clamp(34px, 4.75vw, 58px);
        line-height: 1.2;
        letter-spacing: -0.061em;
        font-weight: 680;
        text-shadow: 0 12px 38px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.58);
      }

      h1 span {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 13px;
        color: var(--gold-soft);
        font-size: clamp(22px, 2.75vw, 32px);
        line-height: 1.24;
        font-weight: 570;
        letter-spacing: -0.044em;
      }

      .question-list {
        display: grid;
        gap: 11px;
        max-width: 760px;
        margin: 0 auto 26px;
      }

      .question-list p {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 15px 20px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: clamp(16px, 1.55vw, 19px);
        font-weight: 560;
        background:
          linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.23), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.038)),
          rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.11);
        box-shadow: 0 16px 46px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.21);
        backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      }

      .hero-warning,
      .flow-alert,
      .golden-time-panel,
      .legal-panel,
      .consult-form,
      .flow-card,
      .case-card,
      .procedure-card,
      .legal-basis-card,
      .media-news-panel,
      .faq-card {
        backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      }

      .hero-warning {
        max-width: 820px;
        margin: 30px auto 0;
        padding: 25px 27px;
        border-radius: 26px;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.08), transparent 42%),
          linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.3), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.27));
        border: 1px solid rgba(236, 68, 80, 0.34);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .hero-warning strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 11px;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: clamp(17px, 1.8vw, 21px);
        font-weight: 610;
        letter-spacing: -0.038em;
      }

      .hero-warning span {
        display: block;
        color: #d8cec7;
        font-size: 15.5px;
        line-height: 1.82;
        font-weight: 380;
      }

      .section-head {
        max-width: 880px;
        margin: 0 auto 38px;
      }

      .section-head.compact {
        margin-top: 48px;
        margin-bottom: 28px;
      }

      .section-head h2 {
        margin-bottom: 18px;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: clamp(28px, 3.25vw, 43px);
        line-height: 1.32;
        letter-spacing: -0.055em;
        font-weight: 650;
      }

      .section-head h2 span {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 9px;
        color: var(--gold-soft);
        font-size: clamp(19px, 2.4vw, 28px);
        font-weight: 540;
      }

      .section-head.compact h2 {
        font-size: clamp(24px, 2.7vw, 34px);
      }

      .section-head p:not(.eyebrow) {
        margin-bottom: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.85;
        font-weight: 370;
      }

      .flow-section {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: none;
        padding: 98px max(18px, calc((100vw - var(--max)) / 2)) 92px;
        border-top: 0 !important;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.08), transparent 34%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 50% 54%, rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.17), transparent 42%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(6, 6, 8, 0), rgba(26, 7, 10, 0.47) 42%, rgba(6, 6, 8, 0.12));
      }

      .flow-alert {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto 34px;
        padding: 22px 24px;
        border-radius: 24px;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 17px;
        font-weight: 590;
        background:
          linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.32), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28)),
          rgba(12, 12, 15, 0.62);
        border: 1px solid rgba(236, 68, 80, 0.28);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .vertical-flow {
        max-width: 760px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: grid;
        gap: 13px;
      }

      .flow-card {
        position: relative;
        padding: 28px 26px;
        border-radius: 26px;
        background:
          linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055), rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.11)),
          rgba(16, 16, 20, 0.78);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.105);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 58px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24);
      }

      .flow-card > span {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-width: 42px;
        height: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        color: var(--gold);
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 620;
        background: rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.22);
      }

      .flow-card h3 {
        margin-bottom: 9px;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 620;
        letter-spacing: -0.046em;
      }

      .flow-card p {
        max-width: 620px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.78;
        font-weight: 370;
      }

      .down-arrow {
        color: var(--red2);
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 620;
        line-height: 1;
        text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(185, 34, 44, 0.42);
      }

      .golden-time-panel {
        max-width: 880px;
        margin: 0 auto 28px;
        padding: 25px 28px;
        border-radius: 28px;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.11), transparent 42%),
          linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.22), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.045)),
          rgba(9, 9, 12, 0.72);
        border: 1px solid rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.18);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .golden-time-panel strong {
        display: block;
        color: var(--gold-soft);
        font-size: clamp(19px, 2.25vw, 26px);
        font-weight: 620;
        letter-spacing: -0.047em;
      }

      .case-marquee-shell {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 10px auto 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        padding: 8px 0 22px;
        mask-image: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, #000 8%, #000 92%, transparent 100%);
      }

      .case-marquee-track {
        display: flex;
        gap: 16px;
        width: max-content;
        animation: caseMarquee 34s linear infinite;
      }

      .case-marquee-shell:hover .case-marquee-track {
        animation-play-state: paused;
      }

      .case-card {
        flex: 0 0 250px;
        width: 250px;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 20px;
        background:
          linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(112, 12, 19, 0.86), rgba(8, 13, 21, 0.96)),
          rgba(18, 18, 22, 0.88);
        border: 1px solid rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.2);
        box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
      }

      .case-image {
        position: relative;
        aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        overflow: hidden;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 50% 18%, rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.15), transparent 36%),
          linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07), rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.14)),
          #141419;
      }

      .case-image::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: auto 0 0;
        height: 32%;
        background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(9, 7, 10, 0.86), transparent);
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      .case-image img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
      }

      .image-fallback {
        position: absolute;
        color: var(--dim);
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 560;
      }

      .case-image img + .image-fallback {
        display: none;
      }

      .case-body {
        min-height: 166px;
        padding: 16px 14px 18px;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(45, 7, 11, 0.3), rgba(5, 8, 13, 0.4));
      }

      .case-body strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 17px;
        font-weight: 620;
      }

      .case-body span {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 9px;
        color: var(--gold-soft);
        font-size: 12.8px;
        font-weight: 560;
        line-height: 1.48;
      }

      .case-body p {
        margin: 0;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
        font-size: 12.8px;
        line-height: 1.62;
        font-weight: 360;
      }

      @keyframes caseMarquee {
        from {
          transform: translateX(0);
        }
        to {
          transform: translateX(calc(-50% - 8px));
        }
      }

      .media-block {
        position: relative;
        margin-top: 66px;
        padding: 50px 0 6px;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      }

      .media-news-panel {
        position: relative;
        max-width: 930px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        overflow: hidden;
        padding: 8px;
        border-radius: 26px;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 12% 0%, rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.11), transparent 34%),
          linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.016)),
          rgba(10, 10, 13, 0.78);
        border: 1px solid rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.11);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .media-news-item {
        position: relative;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
        gap: 18px;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 19px 21px 19px 23px;
        text-align: left;
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.016);
        transition: background 0.22s ease, transform 0.22s ease, box-shadow 0.22s ease;
      }

      .media-news-item::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        top: 18px;
        bottom: 18px;
        width: 3px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gold), rgba(185, 34, 44, 0.7));
        opacity: 0.62;
      }

      .media-news-item + .media-news-item {
        margin-top: 6px;
      }

      .media-news-item:hover {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.12), rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.04));
        transform: translateX(3px);
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.11);
      }

      .media-news-meta {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        margin-bottom: 7px;
        color: #cfc6c0;
        font-size: 12.8px;
        font-weight: 430;
        line-height: 1.35;
      }

      .media-news-meta strong {
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .media-news-meta time {
        color: var(--dim);
      }

      .press-dot {
        width: 6px;
        height: 6px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), #fff2c8);
        box-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.3);
        flex: 0 0 auto;
      }

      .media-news-copy h3 {
        margin: 0 0 6px;
        color: #f5f2ee;
        font-size: clamp(16px, 1.48vw, 19.5px);
        line-height: 1.38;
        letter-spacing: -0.043em;
        font-weight: 610;
      }

      .media-news-copy p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 13.5px;
        line-height: 1.64;
        display: -webkit-box;
        -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
        -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
        overflow: hidden;
        font-weight: 360;
      }

      .media-open-label {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 6px;
        min-width: 92px;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        color: #f2dfbf;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 580;
        white-space: nowrap;
        background: rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.075);
        border: 1px solid rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.21);
      }

      .procedure-section {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: none;
        padding-left: max(18px, calc((100vw - var(--max)) / 2));
        padding-right: max(18px, calc((100vw - var(--max)) / 2));
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 15% 14%, rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.068), transparent 28%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 84% 22%, rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.14), transparent 34%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(6, 6, 8, 0), rgba(18, 7, 10, 0.32), rgba(6, 6, 8, 0));
      }

      .procedure-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 16px;
        width: min(var(--max), 100%);
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .procedure-card {
        position: relative;
        min-height: 226px;
        padding: 27px 24px;
        border-radius: 26px;
        text-align: left;
        overflow: hidden;
        background:
          linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.058), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.018)),
          rgba(16, 16, 20, 0.77);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 58px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24);
      }

      .procedure-card::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        right: -34px;
        top: -34px;
        width: 104px;
        height: 104px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.14), transparent 68%);
      }

      .procedure-card span {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-width: 44px;
        height: 30px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        color: var(--gold);
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 620;
        background: rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.22);
      }

      .procedure-card h3 {
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 21px;
        font-weight: 620;
        line-height: 1.36;
        letter-spacing: -0.048em;
      }

      .procedure-card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 14.5px;
        line-height: 1.76;
        font-weight: 360;
      }

      .legal-panel {
        padding: 42px;
        border-radius: 34px;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.08), transparent 34%),
          linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.14), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04)),
          rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.075);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .legal-basis-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 15px;
      }

      .legal-basis-card {
        padding: 25px 23px;
        border-radius: 24px;
        text-align: left;
        background:
          linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.022)),
          rgba(15, 15, 19, 0.74);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.21);
      }

      .legal-basis-card h3 {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 21px;
        font-weight: 620;
        letter-spacing: -0.045em;
      }

      .legal-basis-card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 14.5px;
        line-height: 1.76;
        font-weight: 360;
      }

      .faq-section {
        padding-top: 88px;
        padding-bottom: 118px;
      }

      .faq-grid {
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .faq-card {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        padding: 26px 26px 25px;
        border-radius: 24px;
        text-align: left;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 0% 0%, rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.08), transparent 30%),
          linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055), rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.06)),
          rgba(15, 15, 19, 0.78);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
      }

      .faq-card::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        top: 22px;
        bottom: 22px;
        width: 3px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gold), rgba(185, 34, 44, 0.78));
        opacity: 0.72;
      }

      .faq-card > span {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-width: 42px;
        height: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 14px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        color: var(--gold);
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 620;
        background: rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.22);
      }

      .faq-card h3 {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 19px;
        line-height: 1.42;
        font-weight: 620;
        letter-spacing: -0.045em;
      }

      .faq-card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 14.5px;
        line-height: 1.76;
        font-weight: 360;
      }

      .consult-section {
        padding-bottom: 110px;
      }

      .consult-form {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 30px;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.075), transparent 36%),
          linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.14), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04)),
          rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24);
        border: 1px solid rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.15);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 15px;
      }

      .consult-form label {
        display: grid;
        gap: 8px;
        color: #f5f2ee;
        font-size: 13.5px;
        font-weight: 520;
      }

      input {
        width: 100%;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        outline: none;
        border-radius: var(--radius-md);
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.27);
        color: #fff;
        padding: 15px 14px;
        font: inherit;
        font-weight: 400;
        text-align: center;
        transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
      }

      input:focus {
        border-color: rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.42);
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.34);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.055);
      }

      input::placeholder {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.34);
      }

      .consult-form button {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
        border: 0;
        border-radius: var(--radius-md);
        padding: 18px 20px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #81111a, #b9222c 54%, #cfa86c 145%);
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 17px;
        font-weight: 620;
        cursor: pointer;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 46px rgba(181, 29, 41, 0.22);
        transition: transform 0.22s ease, filter 0.22s ease;
      }

      .consult-form button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        filter: brightness(1.08);
      }

      .form-notice {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--dim);
        font-size: 12.8px;
        line-height: 1.72;
        font-weight: 360;
      }


      .hp-field {
        position: absolute !important;
        left: -9999px !important;
        width: 1px !important;
        height: 1px !important;
        opacity: 0 !important;
        pointer-events: none !important;
      }

      .form-status {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 22px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-weight: 430;
      }

      .form-status[data-type="success"] {
        color: #e7c895;
      }

      .form-status[data-type="error"] {
        color: #ff7a7a;
      }

      .form-status[data-type="pending"] {
        color: rgba(245, 240, 235, 0.72);
      }

      .consult-form button:disabled {
        cursor: not-allowed;
        opacity: 0.72;
        transform: none;
      }


      .compliance-footer {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: none;
        padding: 72px max(18px, calc((100vw - var(--max)) / 2)) 46px;
        margin-top: -28px;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.07), transparent 34%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(8, 8, 10, 0), rgba(4, 4, 5, 0.72) 34%, rgba(3, 3, 4, 0.96));
      }

      .footer-inner {
        width: min(var(--max), 100%);
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.18fr) minmax(360px, 0.82fr);
        gap: 18px;
        align-items: stretch;
      }

      .footer-notice-panel,
      .business-panel {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 28px;
        background:
          linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.052), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.018)),
          rgba(11, 11, 14, 0.82);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.105);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 58px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24);
        backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      }

      .footer-notice-panel::before,
      .business-panel::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        pointer-events: none;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 14% 0%, rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.105), transparent 31%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 100% 16%, rgba(143, 18, 27, 0.115), transparent 34%);
      }

      .footer-notice-panel {
        padding: 30px 30px 28px;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .footer-kicker {
        position: relative;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        margin: 0 0 18px;
        color: var(--gold-soft);
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 610;
        letter-spacing: -0.012em;
      }

      .footer-kicker::before {
        content: "";
        width: 7px;
        height: 7px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: var(--gold);
        box-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.34);
      }

      .footer-notice-copy {
        position: relative;
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .footer-notice-copy p {
        margin: 0;
        color: rgba(245, 240, 235, 0.72);
        font-size: 13.5px;
        line-height: 1.78;
        font-weight: 350;
        letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      }

      .business-panel {
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: left;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 20px;
      }

      .business-list {
        position: relative;
        margin: 0;
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .business-list div {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 118px minmax(0, 1fr);
        gap: 12px;
        align-items: start;
      }

      .business-list dt,
      .business-list dd {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 13.2px;
        line-height: 1.62;
      }

      .business-list dt {
        color: rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.82);
        font-weight: 560;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .business-list dd {
        color: rgba(245, 240, 235, 0.78);
        font-weight: 370;
      }

      .policy-links {
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .policy-links a {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 34px;
        padding: 7px 11px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        color: rgba(245, 240, 235, 0.78);
        font-size: 12.2px;
        font-weight: 470;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.048);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.085);
        transition: background 0.22s ease, color 0.22s ease, transform 0.22s ease;
      }

      .policy-links a:hover {
        transform: translateY(-1px);
        color: #fff;
        background: rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.1);
      }

      /* 최종 정리: 전체 섹션 간격, 카드 호버, 스크롤 페이드인 */
      .section {
        scroll-margin-top: 72px;
      }

      .hero-copy,
      .section-head,
      .flow-alert,
      .golden-time-panel,
      .vertical-flow,
      .case-marquee-shell,
      .media-block,
      .procedure-grid,
      .legal-panel,
      .consult-form,
      .footer-inner {
        will-change: transform, opacity;
      }

      .flow-card,
      .procedure-card,
      .legal-basis-card,
      .case-card,
      .media-news-item,
      .footer-notice-panel,
      .business-panel,
      .consult-form,
      .hero-warning,
      .golden-time-panel,
      .legal-panel,
      .faq-card {
        transition:
          transform 0.28s ease,
          border-color 0.28s ease,
          box-shadow 0.28s ease,
          background 0.28s ease;
      }

      .flow-card:hover,
      .procedure-card:hover,
      .legal-basis-card:hover,
      .faq-card:hover,
      .footer-notice-panel:hover,
      .business-panel:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        border-color: rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.22);
        box-shadow: 0 26px 72px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      }

      .consult-form:hover,
      .legal-panel:hover,
      .golden-time-panel:hover,
      .hero-warning:hover {
        border-color: rgba(207, 168, 108, 0.24);
        box-shadow: 0 28px 82px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.42);
      }

      .fade-reveal {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
        filter: blur(5px);
        transition:
          opacity 0.82s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1),
          transform 0.82s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1),
          filter 0.82s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        transition-delay: var(--reveal-delay, 0ms);
      }

      .fade-reveal.is-visible {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
        filter: blur(0);
      }

      .fade-reveal.reveal-left {
        transform: translateX(-28px);
      }

      .fade-reveal.reveal-right {
        transform: translateX(28px);
      }

      .fade-reveal.reveal-left.is-visible,
      .fade-reveal.reveal-right.is-visible {
        transform: translateX(0);
      }

      @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
        .fade-reveal,
        .fade-reveal.reveal-left,
        .fade-reveal.reveal-right {
          opacity: 1 !important;
          transform: none !important;
          filter: none !important;
          transition: none !important;
        }

        .case-marquee-track {
          animation: none !important;
        }
      }

      .bottom-cta {
        position: fixed;
        left: 50%;
        bottom: 16px;
        z-index: 60;
        width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 24px));
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 16px;
        padding: 14px;
        border-radius: 22px;
        background: rgba(11, 11, 14, 0.88);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.13);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 72px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.46);
        backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      }

      .bottom-cta strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 15.5px;
        font-weight: 610;
        letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      }

      .bottom-cta span {
        display: block;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 12.8px;
      }

      .bottom-cta nav {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(104px, 1fr));
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .bottom-cta a {
        min-width: 104px;
        padding: 12px 15px;
        border-radius: var(--radius-md);
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 570;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.075);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        transition: transform 0.22s ease, background 0.22s ease;
      }

      .bottom-cta a:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.115);
      }

      .bottom-cta a:first-child {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #741019, #b9222c);
        border-color: transparent;
      }

      .bottom-cta a:nth-child(3) {
        color: #120707;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #cfa86c, #f1d19b);
        border-color: transparent;
      }

      .mobile-only {
        display: none;
      }

      @media (max-width: 1020px) {
        .procedure-grid,
        .legal-basis-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          max-width: 720px;
          margin-left: auto;
          margin-right: auto;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 720px) {
        .page-shell {
          padding-bottom: 142px;
        }

        .top-alert {
          font-size: 11.5px;
          line-height: 1.45;
        }

        .section {
          width: min(100% - 28px, var(--max));
          padding: 64px 0;
        }

        .flow-section,
        .procedure-section {
          width: 100%;
          padding-left: 14px;
          padding-right: 14px;
        }

        .hero {
          min-height: auto;
          padding-top: 44px;
          padding-bottom: 62px;
        }

        .hero-brand-mark img {
          max-width: 84vw;
          height: clamp(82px, 22vw, 118px);
        }

        .pc-only {
          display: none;
        }

        .mobile-only {
          display: block;
        }

        h1 {
          font-size: clamp(30px, 8.2vw, 42px);
          line-height: 1.22;
          font-weight: 560;
          letter-spacing: -0.055em;
        }

        h1 span {
          font-size: clamp(20px, 5.3vw, 27px);
          font-weight: 520;
        }

        .question-list p {
          padding: 14px 16px;
          border-radius: 17px;
          font-size: 15px;
          font-weight: 520;
          line-height: 1.42;
        }

        .hero-warning,
        .flow-alert,
        .golden-time-panel,
        .legal-panel,
        .consult-form {
          padding: 22px 18px;
          border-radius: 22px;
        }

        .section-head h2 {
          max-width: 96vw;
